### Current Preview:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65661241/120290093-9fd58c00-c2df-11eb-9dff-043b33a34065.png)




**Status**
- [x] Basic HTML export tool for the loaded timeline 
- [x] Add more features to this (like file handling, handling reply events, etc.)
- [x] Extend the implementation to support going back (from the beginning or for a given number of messages)
- [x] Additional format - Plain Test
- [x] Additional format - JSON
- [x] Create a UI to interact with the tool
- [x] Write tests


(a part of gsoc'21)

Closes vector-im/element-web#2630

Signed-off-by: Jaiwanth jaiwanth2011@gmail.com


<!-- CHANGELOG_PREVIEW_START -->
---
